XML-Filter-Normalize

This module is a filter for use with XML::SAX.  It tries to clean up a
stream of SAX events in order to correctly comply with the SAX
specifications.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

